        <source>setByTypeByWeight(_byTypeByWeight : Boolean) updating;
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
15 Jan 2024	jlirs1	TFS 61640 EUP Release Request by Type by Weight
